title: Jewels of the Oracle
description:
Title: Jewels of the Oracle
Genre: Puzzle / Point and click
Released: 1995
Developer: ELOI Productions
Publisher: DreamCatcher Interactive 

Jewels of the Oracle is an adventure/puzzle games from the '90s with pre-rendered 3D environments and interactive devices to play with and solve.

Praised for it's graphics and music, Jewels has been called one of the best puzzle games on CD-ROM. It combines ancient games and puzzles along with some new ones and turns them into point and click devices made of rock and wood
